item.title: Eduardo da Silva Amazing Volley goal! (06/11) Shakhtar Donetsk Vs Krivbass
item.description:
Eduardo da Silva Amazing Volley goal! (06/11) Shakhtar Donetsk Vs Krivbass
goal.com Fresh from scoring the winner against his old club Arsenal on Wednesday night in the Champions League, Eduardo netted a brilliant strike in Shakhtar Donetsk's league match at Kryvbas today. The Cro-Zilian has now scored five goals in 14 appearances for Shakhtar and his move from Arsene Wenger's Arsenal appears to be paying off. Eduardo is playing more regularly and beginning to find the form that made his name when he was at Dinamo Zagreb. Today's excellent goal (reminiscent of Zinedine Zidane's in the 2002 Champions League final) saw Eduardo give Shakhtar the lead at Kryvbas on the stroke of half-time with an impressive volley with his right foot. Eduardo da Silva's excellent volley v Kryvbas can be seen on this video. Shakhtar won the match 2-0, Jadson adding a second on 88 minutes to see them go five points clear at the top of the table in Ukraine. globoesporte.globo.com Eduardo da Silva fez um golaço hoje na vitória do Shakhtar Donetsk por 2 a 0 sobre o Kryvbas Krivyi Rig, fora de casa, pelo Campeonato Ucraniano Супергол Едуардо да Силвы Шахтер Донецк - Кривбасс
